txt.en: 'A disease in Kh没tra? Where do you hail from, stranger?'

'Where are you from, stranger? Not from Gondor, I presume. We have no need for their kind here.

'Help? We don't need help here, and certainly not from outsiders.

'If you want to help, go talk to my fisherfolk and get my people some fish that don't reek of death. Bah. Off with you.'
